{"type":"message","id":"4867eed8","parentId":"379d1dd4","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:00:24.566Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 14:00 GMT+2] MASTER PROTOCOL & BOT CONTROL INTEGRATION (Pro Stream).\n\n1.  **Create MASTER_PROTOCOL.md (`docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`):**\n    *   Synthesize all learnings: SACS-2026, Atomic Rollback, Spec-First, Observability, HFT Rules.\n    *   *Directive:* This is the \"Supreme Law\".\n\n2.  **Bot Control Integration (`src/agent_wrapper.py`):**\n    *   Add CLI commands: `/start_bot`, `/stop_bot`, `/status`.\n    *   *Implementation:* Use `subprocess.Popen` (detached) or `openclaw process` tool logic to manage the `main.py` execution.\n    *   *Persistence:* Store PID in `bot.pid`.\n\n3.  **Model Optimization Strategy (Gemini 3 Pro/Flash):**\n    *   *Gemini 3 Pro (Architect/Trader):*\n        *   Context: 1M tokens allows loading full historical price data for pattern recognition.\n        *   Settings: `temperature=0.7` (Creative Strategy), `top_p=0.95`.\n    *   *Gemini 3 Flash (Validator/Signal):*\n        *   Role: Signature validation, quick syntax checks.\n        *   Settings: `temperature=0.0` (Deterministic), `top_p=0.1` (Strict).\n\n4.  **Output:**\n    *   Confirmation of `MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`.\n    *   Control commands help text.\n    *   Model tuning report."}],"timestamp":1771156824565}}
