{"type":"message","id":"50d1e100","parentId":"a81ae604","timestamp":"2026-02-15T12:02:44.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Concluding the Response**\n\n\\n\\n\n\nOkay, I've finished the tasks at hand. It's time to craft the final response. I've noted that `src/main.py` is currently just a placeholder. Reviewing the prompt again, I'll ensure my output includes the required components: Confirmation of MASTER_PROTOCOL.md, the control commands help text, and the model tuning report. I'll make sure the format aligns perfectly.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"**Mission Complete.**\n\nI have successfully established the Master Protocol and implemented the Bot Control Integration.\n\n### 1. MASTER PROTOCOL (`docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`)\nThe **\"Supreme Law\"** document has been created, synthesizing all critical directives:\n*   **SACS-2026:** Mandating 99.99% uptime and full 12-agent fleet integrity.\n*   **Atomic Rollback:** Enforcing \"The Rule of Two\" (Snapshot + Verification Gate).\n*   **Spec-First:** \"Code follows Documentation\" is now the law.\n*   **HFT Rules:** Hard limits on drawdown (2%) and position sizing (5%).\n*   **Observability:** Mandatory JSON logging and latency tracking.\n\n### 2. Bot Control Integration (`src/agent_wrapper.py`)\nThe control interface is live. It manages the lifecycle of the trading bot (currently a placeholder in `src/main.py`) using detached subprocesses for true background execution.\n\n**Control Commands:**\n*   `/start_bot`: Launches the bot in a detached process, saving PID to `src/bot.pid`.\n*   `/stop_bot`: Safely terminates the bot using the stored PID.\n*   `/status`: Checks process health and PID file integrity.\n\n**Usage:**\n```bash\npython src/agent_wrapper.py /start_bot\npython src/agent_wrapper.py /status\npython src/agent_wrapper.py /stop_bot\n```\n\n### 3. Model Optimization Strategy\nDefined and codified within the Master Protocol (Section 7).\n\n| Model | Role | Configuration | Purpose |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| **Gemini 3 Pro** | **Architect / Trader** | `Temp: 0.7`, `Top_P: 0.95` | **Creative Strategy.** Uses 1M token context for deep historical pattern recognition and complex market analysis. |\n| **Gemini 3 Flash** | **Validator / Signal** | `Temp: 0.0`, `Top_P: 0.1` | **Strict Safety.** Deterministic execution for signature validation, syntax checks, and pre-trade guardrails. |","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":12692,"output":555,"cacheRead":11684,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13247,"cost":{"input":0.025384,"output":0.00666,"cacheRead":0.0023368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0343808}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771156955834}}
